rs.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9998853596218141, \"rank\": 0.00011465224094518099, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The injury\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's artistic all-around gymnastics events\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite her setback, Escalera managed to finish her routine and was the Mexican with the best score, 12.800, on the apparatus.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\", \"score\": 0.9680902287119705, \"rank\": 0.03294693507050638, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her setback\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"Escalera\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"the best score\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"the apparatus\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris Olympics 2024 But moments after her dismount, Escalera began to cry from the pain and required help from her coach to move away from the competition area and off the side of the stage.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"her dismount\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"Escalera\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"required help\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition area\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was then picked up and carried to a chair.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chair\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I had said I wasn't going to participate, but I had to take as many pills as I could to be able to do it and I am very happy because I was able to fulfill my dream,' Escalera said after making her Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as many pills\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"Escalera\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic debut\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They say that the stage is a painkiller, I am in a lot of pain, but it was the last routine, so I had to give everything.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"a painkiller\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"the last routine\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Every time I put my foot on the bar it was pain; I just prayed to get through the routine healthy.'\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my foot\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from